        {
          "quote": "- O2-rich atmosphere cases are not fully ruled out by current data.",
          "line_ref": "L36"
        }
      ],
      "caveat": "Because multiple atmosphere scenarios can fit the present observations, broader wavelength coverage and/or repeated observations are needed to better discriminate compositions."
    }
  ]
